title: AHS Apocalypse THE Death: Real or Vision?
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: It has to be a Vision, I mean if that was really Cordelia's death, do you really think they'd put that HUGE of a spoiler into the trailer?

Cordelia can't get eaten by damn zombies
Definitely think it was a vision and that explosion at the end is the witches showing up at the bunker

Yesterday I thought of a season called "Haven" where there is a big infection or apocalypse & everyone goes to this Haven to stay safe. My idea & Apocalypse are kind of the same except Apocalypse is in a mansion underground, not a village, sunshine, swamps, & flowers.
